    <text x="350" y="278" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">최악의 경우로 잡아 두던 여유 용량을 실제 사용량 기준으로 되돌려</text>
    <text x="350" y="298" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">같은 하드웨어에서 더 많은 처리량 · 더 낮은 계약 호출 비용</text>
  </g>
  <text x="350" y="340" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Besu EVM 엔진도 25.2.2로 상향</text>
  <text x="350" y="382" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">출처: 헤데라 HIP-1249 문서, 헤데라 릴리스 노트, 빗썸 공지(2026년 7월 8일)</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="en">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="32" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">HIP-1249: coarse gas ceiling → per-operation pricing</text>
  <text x="175" y="70" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Before (v0.74)</text>
  <text x="525" y="70" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">After (HIP-1249)</text>
  <g font-family="sans-serif">
    <rect x="30" y="86" width="290" height="140" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <text x="175" y="120" fill="#f87171" font-size="15" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle">Single gas ceiling</text>
    <text x="175" y="150" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle">15M gas/sec (flat)</text>
    <text x="175" y="176" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">applied at frontend + backend</text>
    <text x="175" y="202" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">min 80% charge per call</text>
    <rect x="380" y="86" width="290" height="140" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <text x="525" y="120" fill="#4ade80" font-size="15" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle">Ops-per-second throttle</text>
    <text x="525" y="150" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" text-anchor="middle">priced by actual opcode cost</text>
    <text x="525" y="176" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">enforced at consensus layer only</text>
    <text x="525" y="202" fill="#4ade80" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">80% minimum charge removed</text>
    <rect x="30" y="252" width="640" height="60" rx="10" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1"/>
    <text x="350" y="278" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">Reserved worst-case headroom is returned to actual-usage budgeting:</text>
    <text x="350" y="298" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">more throughput on the same hardware, cheaper contract calls</text>
  </g>
  <text x="350" y="340" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Besu EVM engine also raised to 25.2.2</text>
  <text x="350" y="382" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Sources: Hedera HIP-1249 docs, Hedera release notes, Bithumb notice (July 8, 2026)</text>
</svg>
</div>
